<<<"},"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/readme":{"title":"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/readme","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"; Solution plugin
There are many questions and answers in [[TW Google forum|https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/tiddlywiki]], and [[TW Talk|http://talk.tiddlywiki.org/]] some of them shows elegant solution to raised questions and worth to be documented in a manner to be accessible easily later on.

Solution is a small plugin to create solution tiddlers. It adds a button to page controls, on click, creates a tiddler tagged with `solution`, contains `keywords`, `responder`, and `url` fields. It then uses a view template to show the `responder` (author), reference post (`url`), and the `keywords` in a semantic way.

The `keywords` field acts like tags, so, clicking on them shows a list of all tiddlers tagged with this keyword or has this keyword in its `keywords` field.

; Code and demo
For learning plugin features, syntax, tutorial and examples see the plugin demo and code pages

* Demo: https://kookma.github.io/TW-Solution/
* Code: https://github.com/kookma/TW-Solution
"},"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/stylesheet/header-segment":{"title":"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/stylesheet/header-segment","tags":"$:/tags/Stylesheet","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":".tc-btn-invisible.solution-keywords {
	display: inline-block;
	padding: 0.16em 0.7em;
	font-size: 0.9em;
	font-weight: normal;
	line-height: 1.2em;
	white-space: nowrap;
	vertical-align: baseline;
	border-radius: 1em;
	color: #333333;
	background-color:#fff12ea1;
}
/*remove the blue border on button focus */
.tc-btn-invisible.solution-keywords {
	outline:none;
} 
.solution-header{
	background-color: <<colour table-header-background>>;
	border-color: <<colour table-footer-background>>;
	padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
	border-radius: 0.25rem;	
}"},"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/templates/keywords":{"title":"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/templates/keywords","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"<!-- filter tiddlers tagged with current keyword, or has the keyword in its keywords field. -->
\define mainFilter() [tag<currentTiddler>] [search:keywords<currentTiddler>]

<$set name="transclusion" value=<<qualify "$:/state/solution/popup/keyword">> >
<$button class="tc-btn-invisible solution-keywords" popup=<<transclusion>> dragFilter=<<mainFilter>> >
<$text text=<<currentTiddler>>/>
</$button>
<$reveal state=<<transclusion>> type="popup" position="below" animate="yes" class="tc-drop-down">
<$link/>
<hr>
<!-- dislay all tiddlers tagged with kwd or have kwd in their keywords field -->
<$list filter=<<mainFilter>> template="$:/core/ui/ListItemTemplate" />
</$reveal>
</$set>"},"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/ui/Buttons/solution":{"title":"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/ui/Buttons/solution","caption":"{{$:/plugins/kookma/solution/image/question-circle.svg}} {{$:/language/Buttons/Solution/Caption}}","description":"{{$:/language/Buttons/Solution/Hint}}","list-before":"$:/plugins/kookma/shiraz/ui/Buttons/SwitchPalette","tags":"$:/tags/PageControls","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"\define new-solution()
<$action-sendmessage 
    $message="tm-new-tiddler"
    keywords=""
    tags={{{ [[solution]] [{$:/config/solution/extra-tags}enlist-input[]] +[format:titlelist[]join[ ]] }}}
    responder=""
    url="" />
\end


<$button 
 actions=<<new-solution>> 
 tooltip={{$:/language/Buttons/Solution/Hint}} 
 aria-label={{$:/language/Buttons/Solution/Caption}} 
 class=<<tv-config-toolbar-class>> >
<$list filter="[<tv-config-toolbar-icons>prefix[yes]]">
{{$:/plugins/kookma/solution/image/question-circle.svg}}
</$list>
<$list filter="[<tv-config-toolbar-text>prefix[yes]]">
<span class="tc-btn-text"><$text text={{$:/language/Buttons/Solution/Caption}}/></span>
</$list>
</$button>"},"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/ui/ControlPanel/Settings":{"title":"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/ui/ControlPanel/Settings","caption":"Solution","tags":"$:/tags/ControlPanel/SettingsTab $:/tags/MoreSideBar","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"These settings let you customise the behaviour of Solution plugin.

---

;Show Solution settings in more sidebar
:<$checkbox tiddler="$:/plugins/kookma/solution/ui/ControlPanel/Settings" tag="$:/tags/MoreSideBar"> Show settings in more sidebar</$checkbox>

;Extra tags
: <label style="margin-right:5px;">Tags to be added to new solutions tiddler</label><$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/solution/extra-tags" tag=input default="" placeholder="e.g. myTag [[Tag with Space]]"/>
"},"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/viewtemplates/header-segment":{"title":"$:/plugins/kookma/solution/viewtemplates/header-segment","list-before":"$:/core/ui/ViewTemplate/body","tags":"$:/tags/ViewTemplate","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"<$list filter="[all[current]tag[solution]]">
<div class="solution-header">
<$set name=responders tiddler=<<currentTiddler>> field="responder" emptyValue="[[Not set yet]]">
''Ref'': <a href={{!!url}} target="_blank"><$list filter="[enlist<responders>join[, ]]" variable=item><$text text=<<item>> /></$list></a><br>
''Keywords'': <$list filter={{!!keywords}} template="$:/plugins/kookma/solution/templates/keywords" />
</$set>
</div>
</$list>


"}}}
